high_descs: move slightly to the right to face the counter between the two sinks
pick up the bottle of nail polish from the counter
move slightly to the left to face the sink on the left
open the right cabinet door underneath the sink on the left, put the nail polish in to the cabinet and close the door
turn around and move to the toilet, going around to face the left side of the toilet
pick up the bottle of nail polish that is on the back of the toilet
move back around the toilet and to the sink that is on the left side of the counter
open the right cabinet door that is underneath the left sink and put the bottle of nail polish in to the cabinet to the right of the first bottle of polish, close the door
anns.task_desc: put two bottles of nail polish in to the cabinet under the sink

high_descs: Go to the right to the counter in between the two sinks.
Pick up the candle that is on the counter.
Turn around, go forward, turn back around to face the sink.
Put the candle in the right hand cabinet beneath the leftmost sink.
Turn to the right, go around to the other side of the toilet.
Pick up the candle from the back of the toilet.
Go around to the other side of the toilet, turn to face the sink.
Put the candle in the right hand cabinet beneath the leftmost sink to the right of the other candle.
anns.task_desc: Put two candles in a cabinet.

high_descs: walk right to face counter between sinks
pick up candle stick from counter
back up to face cabinets beneath sink
put candle stick inside cabinet
turn around to face toilet
pick up candle stick from toilet tank top
walk to face cabinets beneath sink
put candle stick inside cabinet
anns.task_desc: put two candle sticks inside cabinet
